Package: rspivot
Type: Package
Title: View data frames as Shiny pivot tables
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2),
    shiny (>= 0.13)
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 0.7.4),
    tidyr (>= 0.7.2),
