Version: 0.1.1.9003
Author: Ryan Timpe <ryan.timpe at gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ryan", "Timpe", email = "ryan.timpe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: RStudio add-in to review dataframe objects as pivot tables. Can export "snapshots" of those tables as tribbles. Also includes quicktibble() Addin to manually create data frames.
